<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="71" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="71">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="71">
Medium-sized bee (total length 10-13 mm in both sexes, wing length c. 8 mm in females) with orange brown hairy thorax and dark abdomen with white hairy tergite margins (Fig. 4
<normalizedToken originalValue="a–b">a-b</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
